        <div class="gmail_quote">On Tue, May 26, 2015 at 6:59 PM, Jeff
          Squyres (jsquyres) <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:jsquyres@cisco.com" target="_blank">jsquyres@cisco.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>
          <blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">This line:<br>
            <br>
                <a href="https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/blob/master/config/ompi_check_mxm.m4#L41" target="_blank">https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/blob/master/config/ompi_check_mxm.m4#L41</a><br>
            <br>
            doesn&#39;t check to see if $ompi_check_mxm_libdir is empty.<br>
            <div>
              <div><br>
                <br>
                &gt; On May 26, 2015, at 11:50 AM, Mike Dubman &lt;<a href="mailto:miked@dev.mellanox.co.il" target="_blank">miked@dev.mellanox.co.il</a>&gt;
